The travel articles were written by me  
Charles "Chuck" Taylor and I own the copyrights to each story.  
Johnnyjet.com has republished the stories under an false assumed  
name "Charles Smith." and "Chuckie Cheese." I've notified Johnnyjet.com  
about the infringement and asked them to correct it. They have not  
corrected or removed the content.
